Package com.hoddmimes.distributor.bdxgwy

Class BdxGwyOutboundGatewayEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.hoddmimes.distributor.bdxgwy.BdxGwyOutboundGatewayEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BdxGwyOutboundTcpIpConnection.CallbackInterface, java.lang.Runnable
    public class BdxGwyOutboundGatewayEntry
extends java.lang.Thread
implements BdxGwyOutboundTcpIpConnection.CallbackInterface
    Handling the interaction with a remote bdx gateway from which we would like to subscribe/retreive information from. The message interaction is the following DistBdxGwyHello (out), sent to identify ourself. Sent when connection is established DistBdxGwySubscrInterest (out), sent initially to declare local interest. Also sent every time the local interest is updated. DistBdxGwyPingRqst (out), sent periodically to keep the session alive DistBdxGwyUpdateItem (in), updates from remote broadcast gateway DistBdxGwyPingRsp (in), responses from remote broadcast gateway for a previous sent DistBdxGwyPingRqst
